---

This project is based on the work of MTry's homebridge-smart-irrigation:
https://github.com/MTry/homebridge-smart-irrigation

The ETo calculation is based on the FAO-56 Penman-Monteith method as described in:
FAO Irrigation and Drainage Paper No. 56
"Crop Evapotranspiration - Guidelines for computing crop water requirements"
http://www.fao.org/3/X0490E/x0490e00.htm
